213
00:08:57,519 --> 00:08:59,476
<Default><b>you disgusting monster.</b></Default>

214
00:08:59,500 --> 00:09:00,635
<Default><b>A monster?</b></Default>

215
00:09:00,659 --> 00:09:03,316
<Default><b>You're really
calling me a monster?</b></Default>

216
00:09:03,340 --> 00:09:04,716
<Default><b>That's impossible.</b></Default>

217
00:09:04,740 --> 00:09:07,309
<Default><b>In this form, I
am like a god!</b></Default>

218
00:09:09,820 --> 00:09:11,395
<Default><b>[groans]</b></Default>

219
00:09:11,419 --> 00:09:12,635
<Default><b>No.</b></Default>

220
00:09:12,659 --> 00:09:15,676
<Default><b>I'm the monster?</b></Default>

221
00:09:15,700 --> 00:09:16,836
<Default><b>No!</b></Default>

222
00:09:16,860 --> 00:09:18,476
<Default><b>No!</b></Default>

223
00:09:18,500 --> 00:09:21,395
<Default><b>This... this can't be.</b></Default>

224
00:09:21,419 --> 00:09:23,056
<Default><b>It just can't be!</b></Default>

225
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:25,049
<Default><b>[yells]</b></Default>

226
00:09:27,019 --> 00:09:28,980
<Default><b>[thuds]</b></Default>

227
00:09:29,980 --> 00:09:31,155
<Default><b>Atla?</b></Default>

228
00:09:31,179 --> 00:09:32,375
<Default><b>Listen to me.</b></Default>

229
00:09:32,399 --> 00:09:34,155
<Default><b>Focus all your power
on a single point</b></Default>

230
00:09:34,179 --> 00:09:35,916
<Default><b>and then break through.</b></Default>

231
00:09:35,940 --> 00:09:37,905
<Default><b>All right, you got it.</b></Default>

232
00:09:37,929 --> 00:09:40,326
<Default><b>[determined music]</b></Default>

233
00:09:40,350 --> 00:09:42,755
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

234
00:09:42,779 --> 00:09:45,279
<Default><b>Now, whatever you
do, don't let go!</b></Default>

235
00:09:47,299 --> 00:09:48,276
<Default><b>I see.</b></Default>

236
00:09:48,300 --> 00:09:49,515
<Default><b>If I'm not mistaken</b></Default>

237
00:09:49,539 --> 00:09:50,836
<Default><b>there is an
ancient white tiger</b></Default>

238
00:09:50,860 --> 00:09:52,196
<Default><b>battle technique.</b></Default>

239
00:09:52,220 --> 00:09:54,635
<Default><b>They call it Tyrant
Tiger Strike.</b></Default>

240
00:09:54,659 --> 00:09:56,395
<Default><b>Tyran and Lucia.</b></Default>

241
00:09:56,419 --> 00:09:59,226
<Default><b>Are you both
watching this?</b></Default>

242
00:09:59,250 --> 00:10:02,155
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

243
00:10:02,179 --> 00:10:04,620
<Default><b>[yelling]</b></Default>

244
00:10:13,889 --> 00:10:16,330
<Default><b>[roars]</b></Default>

245
00:10:19,779 --> 00:10:20,875
<Default><b>No!</b></Default>

246
00:10:20,899 --> 00:10:23,316
<Default><b>It wasn't supposed
to be this way!</b></Default>

247
00:10:23,340 --> 00:10:26,540
<Default><b>That drug was supposed to make
me the most powerful beast man!</b></Default>

248
00:10:28,139 --> 00:10:30,676
<Default><b>How could they do this?</b></Default>

249
00:10:30,700 --> 00:10:32,260
<Default><b>They all tricked me!</b></Default>

250
00:10:34,480 --> 00:10:35,926
<Default><b>[blasts]</b></Default>

251
00:10:35,950 --> 00:10:37,909
<Default><b>[yells]</b></Default>

252
00:10:40,850 --> 00:10:42,809
<Default><b>[booms]</b></Default>

253
00:10:46,740 --> 00:10:48,260
<Default><b>What the... [yells]</b></Default>

254
00:10:49,179 --> 00:10:50,375
<Default><b>We did it, Brother.</b></Default>

255
00:10:50,399 --> 00:10:52,319
<Default><b>We defeated
that old traitor.</b></Default>

256
00:10:54,379 --> 00:10:56,196
<Default><b>Wait, your body.</b></Default>

257
00:10:56,220 --> 00:10:58,066
<Default><b>It's back to normal.</b></Default>

258
00:10:58,090 --> 00:10:59,067
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

259
00:10:59,091 --> 00:11:01,556
<Default><b>[gentle music]</b></Default>

260
00:11:01,580 --> 00:11:02,716
<Default><b>[ETHAN] Fohl!</b></Default>

261
00:11:02,740 --> 00:11:04,145
<Default><b>Atla!</b></Default>

262
00:11:04,169 --> 00:11:05,645
<Default><b>You did it.</b></Default>

263
00:11:05,669 --> 00:11:07,865
<Default><b>You were able to get revenge
for your father's death.</b></Default>

264
00:11:07,889 --> 00:11:10,019
<Default><b>[gasping]</b></Default>

265
00:11:11,419 --> 00:11:16,905
<Default><b>Father, I finally
avenged you.</b></Default>

266
00:11:16,929 --> 00:11:18,235
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

267
00:11:18,259 --> 00:11:19,436
<Default><b>Oh no, Brother.</b></Default>

268
00:11:19,460 --> 00:11:20,515
<Default><b>Is something wrong?</b></Default>

269
00:11:20,539 --> 00:11:22,155
<Default><b>You're not
hurt, are you?</b></Default>

270
00:11:22,179 --> 00:11:25,076
<Default><b>Atla, you should
probably get off him now.</b></Default>

271
00:11:25,100 --> 00:11:26,615
<Default><b>Why would I do that?</b></Default>

272
00:11:26,639 --> 00:11:29,615
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA] Because I'm pretty
sure you're crushing him.</b></Default>

273
00:11:29,639 --> 00:11:31,995
<Default><b>[ATLA] There's no way
my brother is that weak.</b></Default>

274
00:11:32,019 --> 00:11:34,806
<Default><b>[FILO]
Wow. Fohl's all squished!</b></Default>

275
00:11:34,830 --> 00:11:36,270
<Default><b>[SADEENA] Oh, my.</b></Default>

276
00:11:39,659 --> 00:11:42,316
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
The following day, a search</b></Default>

277
00:11:42,340 --> 00:11:45,755
<Default><b>began for whoever it was that
gave that drug to Jaralis</b></Default>

278
00:11:45,779 --> 00:11:48,596
<Default><b>and talked him
into committing treason.</b></Default>

279
00:11:48,620 --> 00:11:50,765
<Default><b>But they seemed to have
completely vanished</b></Default>

280
00:11:50,789 --> 00:11:53,166
<Default><b>when Jaralis
was defeated.</b></Default>

281
00:11:53,190 --> 00:11:56,566
<Default><b>Instead, it was decided that
we'd investigate the drug.</b></Default>

282
00:11:56,590 --> 00:11:58,919
<Default><b>So I called
on Rat to help.</b></Default>

283
00:12:01,269 --> 00:12:02,645
<Default><b>It seems like
this will certainly</b></Default>

284
00:12:02,669 --> 00:12:04,309
<Default><b>be worth looking into.</b></Default>

285
00:12:05,389 --> 00:12:08,765
<Default><b>[WERNER] I apologize once
again for our harsh words</b></Default>

286
00:12:08,789 --> 00:12:10,549
<Default><b>towards the
white tigers.</b></Default>

287
00:12:11,350 --> 00:12:14,785
<Default><b>You are true people of
Siltvelt, and because of that</b></Default>

288
00:12:14,809 --> 00:12:17,346
<Default><b>we will give you the respect
you both deserve.</b></Default>

289
00:12:17,370 --> 00:12:19,830
<Default><b>[relieved sighs]</b></Default>

290
00:12:22,789 --> 00:12:25,306
<Default><b>That said, since
we won the duel</b></Default>

291
00:12:25,330 --> 00:12:27,326
<Default><b>will you finally
honor our arrangement?</b></Default>

292
00:12:27,350 --> 00:12:30,885
<Default><b>[WERNER] Yes. But I must inform
you that the duel doesn't</b></Default>

293
00:12:30,909 --> 00:12:32,226
<Default><b>actually matter anymore.</b></Default>

294
00:12:32,250 --> 00:12:33,365
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

295
00:12:33,389 --> 00:12:35,365
<Default><b>[ELDER]
There's an ancient legend.</b></Default>

296
00:12:35,389 --> 00:12:38,326
<Default><b>It says that the one who is
able to reveal the true form</b></Default>

297
00:12:38,350 --> 00:12:40,605
<Default><b>of the people
of Siltelt will be known</b></Default>

298
00:12:40,629 --> 00:12:43,846
<Default><b>as "The Hero
of the Time to Come."</b></Default>

299
00:12:43,870 --> 00:12:45,186
<Default><b>[WERNER]
All will be arranged for you</b></Default>

300
00:12:45,210 --> 00:12:47,285
<Default><b>as you have requested</b></Default>

301
00:12:47,309 --> 00:12:49,846
<Default><b>The ship to Q'ten Lo
is being prepared</b></Default>

302
00:12:49,870 --> 00:12:51,826
<Default><b>and it will be
ready in two days.</b></Default>

303
00:12:51,850 --> 00:12:54,686
<Default><b>[stammers]</b></Default>

304
00:12:54,710 --> 00:12:57,566
<Default><b>And all we dare ask is
that you enjoy your time</b></Default>

305
00:12:57,590 --> 00:12:59,285
<Default><b>in Siltvelt until then.</b></Default>

306
00:12:59,309 --> 00:13:02,485
<Default><b>Now, may I suggest that
perhaps you take a tour</b></Default>

307
00:13:02,509 --> 00:13:04,389
<Default><b>of the castle
town together?</b></Default>

308
00:13:05,200 --> 00:13:07,190
<Default><b>[village chatter]</b></Default>

309
00:13:09,669 --> 00:13:11,806
<Default><b>[SADEENA]
I'm so happy for both of you.</b></Default>

310
00:13:11,830 --> 00:13:13,846
<Default><b>[FOHL] Yeah, thanks.</b></Default>

311
00:13:13,870 --> 00:13:16,005
<Default><b>But I'm just happy I was
able to restore my father's</b></Default>

312
00:13:16,029 --> 00:13:17,686
<Default><b>good name, you know?</b></Default>

313
00:13:17,710 --> 00:13:20,005
<Default><b>And I'm just happy that
I was finally able to get</b></Default>

314
00:13:20,029 --> 00:13:21,355
<Default><b>out of that damn castle.</b></Default>

315
00:13:21,379 --> 00:13:22,625
<Default><b>Hero!</b></Default>

316
00:13:22,649 --> 00:13:24,926
<Default><b>[giggles]</b></Default>

317
00:13:24,950 --> 00:13:26,405
<Default><b>Werner and the others
were saying</b></Default>

318
00:13:26,429 --> 00:13:28,806
<Default><b>something about
a big parade.</b></Default>

319
00:13:28,830 --> 00:13:30,485
<Default><b>We can look
into things like that</b></Default>

320
00:13:30,509 --> 00:13:33,926
<Default><b>once our business with Q'ten
Lo and the Phoenix are settled.</b></Default>

321
00:13:33,950 --> 00:13:36,076
<Default><b>But more
importantly, Fohl.</b></Default>

322
00:13:36,100 --> 00:13:37,405
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

323
00:13:37,429 --> 00:13:39,686
<Default><b>There's somewhere you
wanted to go, right?</b></Default>

324
00:13:39,710 --> 00:13:40,806
<Default><b>Is that OK?</b></Default>

325
00:13:40,830 --> 00:13:43,296
<Default><b>Where do you want
to go, Brother?</b></Default>

326
00:13:43,320 --> 00:13:46,296
<Default><b>[somber music]</b></Default>

327
00:13:46,320 --> 00:13:48,245
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

328
00:13:48,269 --> 00:13:52,409
<Default><b>This grave, it belongs
to our parents, doesn't it?</b></Default>

329
00:13:54,429 --> 00:13:56,605
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Now that Fohl
and Atla's parents' honor</b></Default>

330
00:13:56,629 --> 00:14:00,285
<Default><b>was finally restored
upon Jaralis's defeat</b></Default>

331
00:14:00,309 --> 00:14:03,446
<Default><b>their graves were
scheduled to be moved.</b></Default>

332
00:14:03,470 --> 00:14:05,926
<Default><b>But Fohl refused.</b></Default>

333
00:14:05,950 --> 00:14:07,765
<Default><b>He said he knew
that they both would</b></Default>

334
00:14:07,789 --> 00:14:10,446
<Default><b>have wanted
to remain here.</b></Default>

335
00:14:10,470 --> 00:14:12,726
<Default><b>Fohl's sudden growth is
just something that happens</b></Default>

336
00:14:12,750 --> 00:14:15,125
<Default><b>to Demi-humans, I think.</b></Default>

337
00:14:15,149 --> 00:14:19,086
<Default><b>Becoming a beast man and then a
beast, but more than anything</b></Default>

338
00:14:19,110 --> 00:14:21,645
<Default><b>defeating the powerful foe
that killed his parents</b></Default>

339
00:14:21,669 --> 00:14:24,009
<Default><b>was the greatest
catalyst for it.</b></Default>

340
00:14:25,789 --> 00:14:28,659
<Default><b>Atla was extremely
jealous of him.</b></Default>

341
00:14:31,389 --> 00:14:34,466
<Default><b>Now, Fohl and Atla</b></Default>

342
00:14:34,490 --> 00:14:36,346
<Default><b>There's another place
I need to show you two.</b></Default>

343
00:14:36,370 --> 00:14:38,210
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

344
00:14:40,509 --> 00:14:43,485
<Default><b>You're showing us
their parents' home?</b></Default>

345
00:14:43,509 --> 00:14:45,446
<Default><b>Fohl decided
to sell it in order</b></Default>

346
00:14:45,470 --> 00:14:47,605
<Default><b>to pay for all of Atla's
medical treatments</b></Default>

347
00:14:47,629 --> 00:14:49,966
<Default><b>shortly after
their parents passed away.</b></Default>

348
00:14:49,990 --> 00:14:52,005
<Default><b>I'm so sorry, Atla.</b></Default>

349
00:14:52,029 --> 00:14:53,166
<Default><b>It's OK, Brother.</b></Default>

350
00:14:53,190 --> 00:14:55,686
<Default><b>You don't need
to apologize to me.</b></Default>

351
00:14:55,710 --> 00:14:59,005
<Default><b>But the new owner heard
what happened and would</b></Default>

352
00:14:59,029 --> 00:15:00,476
<Default><b>like to return
it to you.</b></Default>

353
00:15:00,500 --> 00:15:01,477
<Default><b>[SADEENA] Really?</b></Default>

354
00:15:01,501 --> 00:15:04,046
<Default><b>What a generous person.</b></Default>

355
00:15:04,070 --> 00:15:07,226
<Default><b>Yeah, it was someone close to
my father who bought the house.</b></Default>

356
00:15:07,250 --> 00:15:09,525
<Default><b>And they paid
a lot for it, too.</b></Default>

357
00:15:09,549 --> 00:15:11,309
<Default><b>That's very
kind of them.</b></Default>

358
00:15:12,509 --> 00:15:13,905
<Default><b>[thuds]</b></Default>

359
00:15:13,929 --> 00:15:15,209
<Default><b>[FILO groans]</b></Default>

360
00:15:15,929 --> 00:15:18,326
<Default><b>The road was all
bumpy, wasn't it?</b></Default>

361
00:15:18,350 --> 00:15:19,966
<Default><b>[FOHL] We made it.</b></Default>

362
00:15:19,990 --> 00:15:21,176
<Default><b>All right.</b></Default>

363
00:15:21,200 --> 00:15:23,686
<Default><b>So which one of these
is your house?</b></Default>

364
00:15:23,710 --> 00:15:27,645
<Default><b>That big one, that couldn't
possibly be it, could it?</b></Default>

365
00:15:27,669 --> 00:15:30,265
<Default><b>[FOHL]
Actually, it is.</b></Default>

366
00:15:30,289 --> 00:15:31,809
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Seriously?</b></Default>

367
00:15:33,639 --> 00:15:35,485
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA]
It's huge.</b></Default>

368
00:15:35,509 --> 00:15:38,446
<Default><b>Somebody put a lot
of thought into these details.</b></Default>

369
00:15:38,470 --> 00:15:41,245
<Default><b>Those windows
remind me of shoji.</b></Default>

370
00:15:41,269 --> 00:15:42,726
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA] Shoji?</b></Default>

371
00:15:42,750 --> 00:15:45,806
<Default><b>It seems similar
to Chinese decor.</b></Default>

372
00:15:45,830 --> 00:15:47,346
<Default><b>[FILO] Master, look!</b></Default>

373
00:15:47,370 --> 00:15:48,686
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

374
00:15:48,710 --> 00:15:51,645
<Default><b>This tiger's eyes
are both missing.</b></Default>

375
00:15:51,669 --> 00:15:53,446
<Default><b>[FOHL]
Yeah, that's right.</b></Default>

376
00:15:53,470 --> 00:15:55,726
<Default><b>We sold anything
worth money.</b></Default>

377
00:15:55,750 --> 00:15:57,346
<Default><b>Even though you
were a rich kid</b></Default>

378
00:15:57,370 --> 00:15:58,826
<Default><b>you still had
it rough, huh?</b></Default>

379
00:15:58,850 --> 00:16:00,645
<Default><b>Would you shut up?</b></Default>

380
00:16:00,669 --> 00:16:02,726
<Default><b>This is my
father's study.</b></Default>

381
00:16:02,750 --> 00:16:05,346
<Default><b>And they actually left
it exactly like it was.</b></Default>

382
00:16:05,370 --> 00:16:07,290
<Default><b>Brings back so
many memories.</b></Default>

383
00:16:08,909 --> 00:16:09,966
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

384
00:16:09,990 --> 00:16:11,826
<Default><b>It looks like
a changing room.</b></Default>

385
00:16:11,850 --> 00:16:14,770
<Default><b>There used to be traditional
white tiger clothing here.</b></Default>

386
00:16:16,590 --> 00:16:18,056
<Default><b>But this is.</b></Default>

387
00:16:18,080 --> 00:16:19,436
<Default><b>That's weird.</b></Default>

388
00:16:19,460 --> 00:16:21,785
<Default><b>Didn't you say before
that you sold everything?</b></Default>

389
00:16:21,809 --> 00:16:23,365
<Default><b>Yeah, so why?</b></Default>

390
00:16:23,389 --> 00:16:25,726
<Default><b>You don't think they
returned it, do you?</b></Default>

391
00:16:25,750 --> 00:16:30,806
<Default><b>I mean, from
my perspective</b></Default>

392
00:16:30,830 --> 00:16:32,926
<Default><b>I had eventually planned
to make enough money</b></Default>

393
00:16:32,950 --> 00:16:34,885
<Default><b>to be able to
buy it all back.</b></Default>

394
00:16:34,909 --> 00:16:36,405
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
That's good, but...</b></Default>

395
00:16:36,429 --> 00:16:39,125
<Default><b>Remember, you still owe me
quite a bit of money, too.</b></Default>

396
00:16:39,149 --> 00:16:40,126
<Default><b>[grimaces]</b></Default>

397
00:16:40,150 --> 00:16:42,046
<Default><b>Seriously,
Master Naofumi?</b></Default>

398
00:16:42,070 --> 00:16:43,047
<Default><b>I know, Atla.</b></Default>

399
00:16:43,071 --> 00:16:44,296
<Default><b>Want to try it on?</b></Default>

400
00:16:44,320 --> 00:16:47,176
<Default><b>Huh? Raphtalia, do you
think it'll make</b></Default>

401
00:16:47,200 --> 00:16:50,635
<Default><b>me as attractive as you were
when you wore your miko outfit?</b></Default>

402
00:16:50,659 --> 00:16:54,816
<Default><b>Hmm. Is that really the only
time I've been attractive?</b></Default>

403
00:16:54,840 --> 00:16:55,976
<Default><b>Who cares.</b></Default>

404
00:16:56,000 --> 00:16:57,976
<Default><b>I'm going to check
out the kitchen.</b></Default>

405
00:16:58,000 --> 00:17:00,836
<Default><b>If we're staying here</b></Default>

406
00:17:00,860 --> 00:17:02,836
<Default><b>Come on. I'm
going to change.</b></Default>

407
00:17:02,860 --> 00:17:05,085
<Default><b>So you need to leave
the room, Brother.</b></Default>

408
00:17:05,109 --> 00:17:06,545
<Default><b>But Atla!</b></Default>

409
00:17:06,569 --> 00:17:09,456
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Raphtalia, you stay
and help her change.</b></Default>

410
00:17:09,480 --> 00:17:11,136
<Default><b>- Atla!
[RAPHTALIA] All right.</b></Default>

411
00:17:11,160 --> 00:17:13,116
<Default><b>I'll come by so I can show
off my fancy outfit later.</b></Default>

412
00:17:13,140 --> 00:17:14,116
<Default><b>Bye!</b></Default>

413
00:17:14,140 --> 00:17:15,117
<Default><b>See you soon.</b></Default>

414
00:17:15,141 --> 00:17:16,255
<Default><b>Whee!</b></Default>

415
00:17:16,279 --> 00:17:17,376
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Everything in the kitchen</b></Default>

416
00:17:17,400 --> 00:17:19,176
<Default><b>has been well
maintained.</b></Default>

417
00:17:19,200 --> 00:17:21,376
<Default><b>We can work with this.</b></Default>

418
00:17:21,400 --> 00:17:22,956
<Default><b>Now we just
need ingredients.</b></Default>

419
00:17:22,980 --> 00:17:23,957
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Shield Hero.</b></Default>

420
00:17:23,981 --> 00:17:25,456
<Default><b>Hmm?</b></Default>

421
00:17:25,480 --> 00:17:28,156
<Default><b>If you'd allow me, I'd like
to make tonight's dinner.</b></Default>

422
00:17:28,180 --> 00:17:29,180
<Default><b>Wha...</b></Default>

423
00:17:30,799 --> 00:17:32,696
<Default><b>[FOHL] Unfortunately</b></Default>

424
00:17:32,720 --> 00:17:35,495
<Default><b>remember much about her
life here or anything</b></Default>

425
00:17:35,519 --> 00:17:37,495
<Default><b>about our mom and dad.</b></Default>

426
00:17:37,519 --> 00:17:40,335
<Default><b>So if possible</b></Default>

427
00:17:40,359 --> 00:17:42,936
<Default><b>I want to at least let
her try some of the meals</b></Default>

428
00:17:42,960 --> 00:17:44,936
<Default><b>that Mom used to make.</b></Default>

429
00:17:44,960 --> 00:17:47,040
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Mom's home cooking, huh?</b></Default>

430
00:17:47,750 --> 00:17:50,726
<Default><b>[gentle music]</b></Default>

431
00:17:50,750 --> 00:17:57,750
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

432
00:18:21,519 --> 00:18:23,240
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

433
00:18:27,890 --> 00:18:29,206
<Default><b>Oh, wow.</b></Default>

434
00:18:29,230 --> 00:18:31,456
<Default><b>I've never tasted
anything like this before.</b></Default>

435
00:18:31,480 --> 00:18:32,535
<Default><b>But it's good.</b></Default>

436
00:18:32,559 --> 00:18:33,696
<Default><b>I see.</b></Default>

437
00:18:33,720 --> 00:18:35,936
<Default><b>Are you going
to keep that on, Atla?</b></Default>

438
00:18:35,960 --> 00:18:38,216
<Default><b>Do you like it</b></Default>

439
00:18:38,240 --> 00:18:39,456
<Default><b>There were some
for Brother, too</b></Default>

440
00:18:39,480 --> 00:18:41,400
<Default><b>that I can get
ready for him.</b></Default>

441
00:18:43,960 --> 00:18:45,416
<Default><b>Hey, Fohl.</b></Default>

442
00:18:45,440 --> 00:18:46,916
<Default><b>Mind if I try something?</b></Default>

443
00:18:46,940 --> 00:18:48,406
<Default><b>Hmm?</b></Default>

444
00:18:48,430 --> 00:18:50,900
<Default><b>[sizzling]</b></Default>

445
00:18:52,630 --> 00:18:54,470
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
What do you think?</b></Default>

446
00:18:57,279 --> 00:18:58,256
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

447
00:18:58,280 --> 00:18:59,815
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
What's missing?</b></Default>

448
00:18:59,839 --> 00:19:02,735
<Default><b>Not enough sweetness
or tang, I think.</b></Default>

449
00:19:02,759 --> 00:19:05,396
<Default><b>The flavoring is off</b></Default>

450
00:19:05,420 --> 00:19:07,735
<Default><b>It was more of a gentle scent
that you could feel right</b></Default>

451
00:19:07,759 --> 00:19:09,616
<Default><b>in the back
of your nose.</b></Default>

452
00:19:09,640 --> 00:19:11,896
<Default><b>Well, if we're going
to replicate flavors like that</b></Default>

453
00:19:11,920 --> 00:19:13,880
<Default><b>with these
seasonings, then...</b></Default>

454
00:19:16,160 --> 00:19:18,660
<Default><b>[sizzling]</b></Default>

455
00:19:19,660 --> 00:19:21,136
<Default><b>[chomping]</b></Default>

456
00:19:21,160 --> 00:19:22,137
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

457
00:19:22,161 --> 00:19:23,196
<Default><b>It's amazing.</b></Default>

458
00:19:23,220 --> 00:19:25,495
<Default><b>[satisfied sigh]</b></Default>

459
00:19:25,519 --> 00:19:26,535
<Default><b>[FILO] Wow!</b></Default>

460
00:19:26,559 --> 00:19:28,075
<Default><b>It looks delicious!</b></Default>

461
00:19:28,099 --> 00:19:29,815
<Default><b>[squealing]</b></Default>

462
00:19:29,839 --> 00:19:32,976
<Default><b>It's a little unusual</b></Default>

463
00:19:33,000 --> 00:19:35,495
<Default><b>This is really
Siltvelt home cooking.</b></Default>

464
00:19:35,519 --> 00:19:37,436
<Default><b>All we need
is local booze.</b></Default>

465
00:19:37,460 --> 00:19:39,575
<Default><b>That's all you
think about, isn't it?</b></Default>

466
00:19:39,599 --> 00:19:42,095
<Default><b>Atla, Fohl worked
real hard to make</b></Default>

467
00:19:42,119 --> 00:19:44,055
<Default><b>this meal just
right for you.</b></Default>

468
00:19:44,079 --> 00:19:45,176
<Default><b>Better eat it all up.</b></Default>

469
00:19:45,200 --> 00:19:46,177
<Default><b>Whoa, hey.</b></Default>

470
00:19:46,201 --> 00:19:47,755
<Default><b>I can't take
all the credit.</b></Default>

471
00:19:47,779 --> 00:19:48,916
<Default><b>You helped a lot, too.</b></Default>

472
00:19:48,940 --> 00:19:50,315
<Default><b>That's not
important now.</b></Default>

473
00:19:50,339 --> 00:19:51,616
<Default><b>I'm really grateful
for everything</b></Default>

474
00:19:51,640 --> 00:19:52,755
<Default><b>you've done, Brother.</b></Default>

475
00:19:52,779 --> 00:19:55,055
<Default><b>But let's just eat, OK?</b></Default>

476
00:19:55,079 --> 00:19:57,035
<Default><b>It's time to eat!</b></Default>

477
00:19:57,059 --> 00:19:58,656
<Default><b>[murmurs excitedly]</b></Default>

478
00:19:58,680 --> 00:20:00,795
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA] It has
an interesting flavor profile.</b></Default>

479
00:20:00,819 --> 00:20:02,366
<Default><b>[FILO] It's better than
the food at the castle!</b></Default>

480
00:20:02,390 --> 00:20:04,216
<Default><b>Atla, will you try
the potatoes</b></Default>

481
00:20:04,240 --> 00:20:06,815
<Default><b>just one more
time, please?</b></Default>

482
00:20:06,839 --> 00:20:07,839
<Default><b>OK.</b></Default>

483
00:20:14,009 --> 00:20:16,255
<Default><b>[FOHL]
So, what do you think?</b></Default>

484
00:20:16,279 --> 00:20:17,896
<Default><b>It's good.</b></Default>

485
00:20:17,920 --> 00:20:19,815
<Default><b>This flavor.</b></Default>

486
00:20:19,839 --> 00:20:21,446
<Default><b>I like the
way it tastes.</b></Default>

487
00:20:21,470 --> 00:20:22,510
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

488
00:20:23,799 --> 00:20:25,055
<Default><b>Makes me happy.</b></Default>

489
00:20:25,079 --> 00:20:27,176
<Default><b>Mom used to make
it all the time.</b></Default>

490
00:20:27,200 --> 00:20:28,896
<Default><b>It smells a
little different.</b></Default>

491
00:20:28,920 --> 00:20:31,436
<Default><b>Did you change it from
the first time I tasted it?</b></Default>

492
00:20:31,460 --> 00:20:32,595
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Not too much.</b></Default>

493
00:20:32,619 --> 00:20:35,295
<Default><b>I just used a few
Melromarc spices.</b></Default>

494
00:20:35,319 --> 00:20:37,916
<Default><b>That's all it takes
to change the flavor this much?</b></Default>

495
00:20:37,940 --> 00:20:40,206
<Default><b>I just figured that if
your mother was a human</b></Default>

496
00:20:40,230 --> 00:20:43,216
<Default><b>then these are some of the
spices that she would've used.</b></Default>

497
00:20:43,240 --> 00:20:44,735
<Default><b>It's still hard
for me to believe</b></Default>

498
00:20:44,759 --> 00:20:47,156
<Default><b>that she was able to figure
it out so quickly.</b></Default>

499
00:20:47,180 --> 00:20:48,565
<Default><b>It's a combination.</b></Default>

500
00:20:48,589 --> 00:20:50,775
<Default><b>It's a dish that blends
parts of both Demi-human</b></Default>

501
00:20:50,799 --> 00:20:55,216
<Default><b>and human cultures</b></Default>

502
00:20:55,240 --> 00:20:57,295
<Default><b>I see.</b></Default>

503
00:20:57,319 --> 00:21:00,095
<Default><b>This just makes me
miss them even more.</b></Default>

504
00:21:00,119 --> 00:21:02,896
<Default><b>Master Naofumi
and Brother</b></Default>

505
00:21:02,920 --> 00:21:05,136
<Default><b>would the two of you
please teach me how</b></Default>

506
00:21:05,160 --> 00:21:06,716
<Default><b>to cook food
like this too?</b></Default>

507
00:21:06,740 --> 00:21:08,025
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

508
00:21:08,049 --> 00:21:10,856
<Default><b>I want to learn so I
can be as good as you.</b></Default>

509
00:21:10,880 --> 00:21:11,857
<Default><b>[laughs]</b></Default>

510
00:21:11,881 --> 00:21:13,095
<Default><b>Yeah!</b></Default>

511
00:21:13,119 --> 00:21:14,456
<Default><b>Of course we can.</b></Default>

512
00:21:14,480 --> 00:21:16,280
<Default><b>Mom would
have loved that.</b></Default>

513
00:21:17,559 --> 00:21:20,015
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] And so we
spent some time at Fohl</b></Default>

514
00:21:20,039 --> 00:21:21,755
<Default><b>and Atla's family home.</b></Default>

515
00:21:21,779 --> 00:21:24,186
<Default><b>[gentle music]</b></Default>

516
00:21:24,210 --> 00:21:30,480
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

517
00:21:31,480 --> 00:21:32,920
<Default><b>Come on, Brother!</b></Default>

518
00:21:38,640 --> 00:21:41,866
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Eventually, we set out</b></Default>

519
00:21:41,890 --> 00:21:45,666
<Default><b>because preparations with
the ship were almost complete.</b></Default>

520
00:21:45,690 --> 00:21:48,156
<Default><b>Make sure that's
taken care of, too!</b></Default>

521
00:21:48,180 --> 00:21:49,180
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

522
00:21:53,089 --> 00:21:54,366
<Default><b>Master Naofumi?</b></Default>

523
00:21:54,390 --> 00:21:58,065
<Default><b>Yeah, we need to head
back to the village.</b></Default>

524
00:21:58,089 --> 00:22:01,289
<Default><b>There, we'll decide
who's going to Q'ten Lo.</b></Default>

525
00:22:05,190 --> 00:22:07,265
<Default><b>[non-English singing]</b></Default>

526
00:22:07,289 --> 00:22:14,289
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

527
00:23:36,650 --> 00:23:39,190
<Default><b>EPISODE 6: LEAVING PORT</b></Default>

